          </p>
          <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-3">
            <a href="/contents/appointments/" class="flex-1 text-center bg-green-mid hover:bg-green-dark text-white font-body font-semibold py-3.5 rounded-full transition-colors duration-200">
